<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - DO_AN</title>
    <link href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="~/css/site.css" rel="stylesheet" asp-append-version="true" />
    <link href="~/DO_AN.styles.css" rel="stylesheet" asp-append-version="true" />
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #495057;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            box-shadow: 0 0.25rem 0.75rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }

        .navbar-brand {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
        }

        main {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #6c757d;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm navbar-light bg-white border-bottom box-shadow">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <a class="navbar-brand" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">DO_AN</a>
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarSupportedContent"
                        aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto mb-2 mb-sm-0">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">Home</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Privacy">Privacy</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <main role="main">
            <section>
                <h1 class="mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam vel odio quis eros tristique venenatis. Proin et ipsum quis nisl consectetur malesuada. Donec lobortis ante a justo sagittis, eget ultricies metus consectetur. Phasellus mollis leo et diam convallis, vel consequat quam suscipit.</p>
                <p>Integer eget enim a nisl vehicula feugiat. Duis euismod venenatis nisl sit amet facilisis. Phasellus eu velit vel nulla fermentum eleifend. Ut ultricies risus in nisi malesuada consequat. Vivamus nec lorem vel magna placerat vestibulum. Nam consequat pharetra ante, a feugiat nunc volutpat at.</p>
            </section>
        </main>
    </div>

    <footer class="border-top footer text-muted mt-5">
        <div class="container">
            &copy; 2024 - DO_AN - <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Privacy" class="text-decoration-none">Privacy</a>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/site.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
    @await RenderSectionAsync("Scripts", required: false)
</body>
</html>
